{"tid":85580,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 豆腐火腩","createTime":"2017-01-18T12:24:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T17:41:11.000Z","uid":74981,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c5c4b5fc99258e2cae2ecac11c1bccea822542c","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:24:41.000Z","msg":"材料:<br />\n布包豆腐2舊 (切件, 然後用油炸好)<br />\n火腩約10舊<br />\n炸枝竹: 1包 (用水浸半個鐘然後隔走d水備用)<br />\n薑片: 數片<br />\n蒜頭: 數瓣<br />\n乾蔥頭切件: 數件<br />\n蔥頭切段: 數條<br />\n蔥段: 數條<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/fe0059940fed4a468f83e535db935afc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Ffe0059940fed4a468f83e535db935afc.jpg&h=c2f517aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n調味:<br />\n蠔油1湯匙<br />\n生抽2茶匙<br />\n糖3份1茶匙<br />\n米酒2湯匙<br />\n<br />\n芡汁:<br />\n水1碗<br />\n1湯匙豆粉加3湯匙水開稀成豆粉水<br />\n<br />\n1. 先炸豆腐. 直接落油在獲, 用大火燒. 由於豆腐比較易痴底, 所以我地要落多少少油, 半煎炸佢. 油燒到好熱, 出撚哂煙, 再用裡面既熱油朗勻個獲, 跟住轉中火, 落豆腐炸. 由於豆腐會出水, 所以落豆腐前請秘走d水先落獲炸, 豆腐落獲時, 一樣會有彈油既情況, 所以大家做哩個步驟要小心d.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/e211aab9e9d0b5f4a88dd5beb6565cef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fe211aab9e9d0b5f4a88dd5beb6565cef.jpg&h=19ad3fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 豆腐炸到一面金黃硬身, 先反另一面再炸至金黃硬身, 然後隔油撈起豆腐.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/584968cd2bc7affad83615d233d7e126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F584968cd2bc7affad83615d233d7e126.jpg&h=17234b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4364830a7287ab5b75012b7d6c9f3b18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4364830a7287ab5b75012b7d6c9f3b18.jpg&h=bca7cb76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 倒剩少少油, 開中火燒熱, 爆香所有薑, 蒜, 乾蔥頭, 蔥頭.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/99fab502f8e25c00168475ed48610c42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F99fab502f8e25c00168475ed48610c42.jpg&h=074cb6f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 沿住個獲邊贊米酒, 哩個時候酒香四溢, 再落火腩爆香<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/20d245a91d10f35788b479938a4ddf77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F20d245a91d10f35788b479938a4ddf77.jpg&h=e5f96700&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 落1碗水, 蠔油1湯匙, 生抽2茶匙, 糖3份1茶匙, 落埋豆腐同枝竹, 大火滾起後, 襟獲蓋, 收細火, 炆10分鐘. 哩個步驟好緊要, 係整個送好唔好食既關健, 炆既時間唔需要長, 細火炆10分鐘已經可以令d火腩軟化, 唔會食落硬掘掘. 火腩透個炆既過程, 唔單止會變得軟熟, 仲會迫出裡面既油脂, 令成味送既味道去到另一個層次. 豆腐, 枝竹亦會因為炆過所以變得更入味.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/788e434ed638114cd28b64fcf516e715.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F788e434ed638114cd28b64fcf516e715.jpg&h=7f09d06a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/905deed54ecf8db75328891e73124201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F905deed54ecf8db75328891e73124201.jpg&h=076afe2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/2640599dfe30e6a22fa733477855a4be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F2640599dfe30e6a22fa733477855a4be.jpg&h=267273c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6. 打開蓋, 你會發現d汁已經收左好多, 哩個時候會幾條蔥段, 再落豆粉水, 邊落邊炒勻, 至汁完全收杰.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/95374f4619c204b29ed6f0b84abb5254.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F95374f4619c204b29ed6f0b84abb5254.jpg&h=8cd50621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/a2a44aeaa343b0e85f2dede929f3a0eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fa2a44aeaa343b0e85f2dede929f3a0eb.jpg&h=2d59e338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/4fc236ffc0fb1342f9ed74f57c26370b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F4fc236ffc0fb1342f9ed74f57c26370b.jpg&h=41c2c47a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n7. 完成, 炒完d汁薄薄地掛係每舊送度, 冇多餘既汁, 亦唔會搞到變哂水, 咁就為之ok啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/5c1f7a4a89046f690b0b4dd3adfdd49e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F5c1f7a4a89046f690b0b4dd3adfdd49e.jpg&h=f9cd3a17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/54d21b219acae09e43d79a998031899e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F54d21b219acae09e43d79a998031899e.jpg&h=668c06fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豆腐火腩其實係一味好好食既送, 不過出面好多d濕鳩餐廳唔撚識煮, 一係就火腩唔夠大舊, 炆完出黎消失哂, 一係就d豆腐唔撚好食, 或者個汁搞撚到水汪汪又冇味, 再唔係就火腩冇炆夠時間, 或者冇炆過, 所以硬過石頭, 咁樣整臭哂豆腐火腩個名, 可惜......"},{"pid":"4a0e8d61a368389308ff23fc98a6fcb4a766c208","tid":85580,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:26:19.000Z","msg":"sofa like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c389d966cd11d2f935328460cd51fa34ef69917","tid":85580,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"睇落又真係幾高汁<br />\n不過如果多啲汁撈飯會正啲"},{"pid":"282923a7e31f01d335d2e0c7b26eb657e234bd2e","tid":85580,"uid":33728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"好似冇乜汁"},{"pid":"eab59026fe864a0c92bb0a626ef4adab66ac1a4a","tid":85580,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:28:07.000Z","msg":"好正呀好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36d2f8837af67f0eb55e5dd7e69e32862348971","tid":85580,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:36:07.000Z","msg":"請唔請老婆？"},{"pid":"ffb849d0f35288f0095bc3c50f7c5cca3b5ad300","tid":85580,"uid":14878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"好撚肚餓啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9403fb5c58b42d6551bf55fca51d5a0b51bf8d39","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sofa like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9f8d83cc115e0a2341743e92dbea9ac52c9d87","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇落又真係幾高汁<br />\n不過如果多啲汁撈飯會正啲</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959a7ff16f495115852b6bfefeaafe87a083fe3e","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:49:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似冇乜汁</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a65430fe4658a87656eda9512414163f1c798e9","tid":85580,"uid":8174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"已follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想巴打教多啲小菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35af3bd06d15670682e79d3fdcb0f67ad344a9bd","tid":85580,"uid":20137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:54:51.000Z","msg":"巴打下次可唔可以教炒米 整到個米粉底脆卜卜 咁"},{"pid":"5c2f8e70aef3c923e39a79fb1bc966bf1f8849c6","tid":85580,"uid":8388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀<br />\n可唔可以教屋企點整到魚香茄子煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2282b7b339e0eb02d35559b793e58a80a25909da","tid":85580,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:56:39.000Z","msg":"呢次高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd0de30cb1b4c72b192d5fe29441e220ca4f262","tid":85580,"uid":44071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:58:50.000Z","msg":"樓主好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我有個豆腐火腩既秘訣<br />\n爆薑葱時加多 1.5 至2茶匙蝦醬<br />\n成件事會有畫龍點睛既效果<br />\n<br />\n樓主下次可以試下"},{"pid":"9e5f5bb8bb3095fcfea3ebc6503304dd14418fec","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正呀好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔錯架, 不過整得唔夠多, 一陣間就被人掃哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b054de55512ec844f899d0bdf8debe839caa55","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:02:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請唔請老婆？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d30fcddfa4a3b19f617dbd6c10ab5c326f41a2f","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚肚餓啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d2cf51978e8526c2398f9b85877a43309fe523e","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想巴打教多啲小菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n盡能力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad008e070e11b0ab2adb10dfc8f6ace5b05231b8","tid":85580,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"高汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8055a4234e06a954a9910fde15bf9e06f018c0b2","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打下次可唔可以教炒米 整到個米粉底脆卜卜 咁</blockquote><br />\n酒樓會用炸, 屋企可以用煎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f21422a29fadc3864e15c316606b8cdac9d8f9","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚正呀<br />\n可唔可以教屋企點整到魚香茄子煲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我安排下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e10f085763eab74c2e3ed4cad3c757c9238fabf8","tid":85580,"uid":58246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:04:22.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99e985e56054d295462c343da413d033531cab00","tid":85580,"uid":55941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbHkbADUdHncDVQagapBQ2vNYCZrxUsBmiZ2CbCqqYYti?filename=q2xBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2xBE.gif&h=d26fee57&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbHkbADUdHncDVQagapBQ2vNYCZrxUsBmiZ2CbCqqYYti?filename=q2xBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2xBE.gif&h=d26fee57&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbHkbADUdHncDVQagapBQ2vNYCZrxUsBmiZ2CbCqqYYti?filename=q2xBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2xBE.gif&h=d26fee57&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbHkbADUdHncDVQagapBQ2vNYCZrxUsBmiZ2CbCqqYYti?filename=q2xBE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2xBE.gif&h=d26fee57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8eb68c660f602b68bd395d7ab695686734c3bbcf","tid":85580,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢次高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}